FreeCAD resultatobjekt: De importerade data kommer att konverteras till ett FreeCAD FEM-resultatobjekt. Obs: den här inställningen behöver det exakta resultatet komponentnamn och därför fungerar det bara korrekt med VTK-filer exporterade från FreeCAD.

Selects the how the output of the branch is determined:

Passthrough: The branches output is the same as its input, no matter what the branch child filter do.

Append: The branches output is a collection of all child filter: it appends child outputs together and offers this as branch output.

']

Selects the how the output of the branch is determined:

Passthrough: The branches output is the same as its input, no matter what the branch child filter do.

Append: The branches output is a collection of all child filter: it appends child outputs together and offers this as branch output.

Väljer hur filialens utdata ska bestämmas:

Genomströmning: Grenens utdata är samma som dess indata, oavsett vad grenens underordnade filter gör.
